[Fol. 132vb] This book was completed on the 13<hi rend="apices">th</hi> of Taḫśaś, 1975 A.M. ʿAmätä Maryam Gä[brä] Mäs[qäl] (from) ʾUra had it written with her money, 320 Bǝrr, and donated it to the tabot of Qirqos ʾUra so that it might be for her the guide towards eternal life, together with all our fathers and brothers: Gäbrä Mäsqäl, Gäbrä Giyorgis, Wälättä Ḥǝywät, Wälättä Ṣadǝqan [and] ʾAmätä Maryam. He who stole it or erased its (text) shall be excommunicated by the authority of Peter and Paul for ever and ever. Amen and amen. So be it, so be it.
</foreign>
